dcterms:description: DBP15K contains three cross-lingual datasets constructed from the multilingual version of DBpedia, including DBPZH−EN (Chinese to English), DBPJA−EN (Japanese to English), and DBPFR−EN (French to English).

dcterms:description: DWY100K is extracted from DBpedia, Wikidata, and YAGO3. It has two monolingual datasets: DWYWD (DBpedia-Wikidata) and DWYYG (DBpedia-YAGO3). Each dataset has 100,000 reference entity alignments and more than nine hundred thousand triples.
dcterms:title: DWY100K
